<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<knowl mode="exercise" xmlns="https://spatext.clontz.org" version="0.2">
    <intro>
        <p>
For each of the following Initial Value Problems (IVPs), designate the following:
        </p>
        <list>
            <item><p>its Ordinary Differential Equation (ODE)</p></item>
            <item><p>its Initial Value or Values (IVs)</p></item>
            <item><p>the order of the IVP</p></item>
            <item><p>its independent variable</p></item>
            <item><p>its dependent variable</p></item>
            <item><p>whether its solution is implicit or explicit</p></item>
        </list>
        <p>
Then show how to verify that its solution is valid.
        </p>
    </intro>
    <!-- {{#ivps}} -->
        <knowl>
            <content>
                <p>
                    IVP:
                    <m>
                        {{ode}};\qquad
                        {{y}}({{t0}})=
                        {{y0}}{{#yp0}},
                            {{y}}'({{t0}})=
                            {{yp0}}
                        {{/yp0}}
                    </m>
                </p>
                <p>Solution: <m>{{sol}}</m></p>
            </content>
            <outtro>
                <list>
                    <item><p>ODE: <m>{{ode}}</m></p></item>
                    <item><p>IV(s): <m>
                        {{y}}({{t0}})={{y0}}
                        {{#yp0}},{{y}}'({{t0}})={{yp0}}{{/yp0}}
                        </m></p></item>
                    <item><p>Order: {{order}}</p></item>
                    <item><p>Independent variable: <m>{{t}}</m></p></item>
                    <item><p>Dependent variable: <m>{{y}}</m></p></item>
                    <item><p>The solution <m>{{sol}}</m> is {{ex_im}}.</p></item>
                </list>
            </outtro>
        </knowl>
    <!-- {{/ivps}} -->
</knowl>
